'''Interference boxes''' or '''i-boxes''' were small scanner- and communications-jamming devices used by the [[Brotherhood of Darkness/Legends|Brotherhood of Darkness]] near the end of the [[New Sith Wars]].

Each [[Squad/Legends|squad]] in the [[Gloom Walkers]] carried one.

